n the forward steel laser mirror.  This telescope will contain 6 10 x magnifying lenses<br>in a line,and can super concentrate/focus  the laser beam by a magnification factor of 1 million on the target. <br> , <br>5.You pump the laser by exploding an A-bomb, or H-Bomb<br>inside the cavern. The xrays from the nuclear explosion <br>will go through the shaft/ tunnel into the laser tubes.<br> There they will cause the laser tubes to lase and create an xray laser beam.<br>6. The xray laser array will be capable of converting<br>from 10% to  50% of the xray input from the nuclear explosion into an xray laser beam.If I explode a 20-50<br> megaton H-bomb in chamber,  I will then release up to<br>9 * 10 the 17 power joules/ watts of energy. At least 10%<br>of this energy will be then be  converted into a pulsed x ray laser beam by the xray laser tube array. That is a 10 to the<br>17 power watt/joule laser pulse that will last a small fraction<br>of a second in time. If this laser beam were used as a laser weapon it coluld do extreme  damage to its target in theory.<br><br>TIm<br><br>beam<br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#333333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub97.ezboard.com/utmayes1965.showPublicProfile?language=EN>tmayes1965</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Space Cadet</span><br>  Posts: 36<br> <font color=#6F6F6F>(7/12/02 12:21:00 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub97.ezboard.com/fnuclearspacefrm20.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=27.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: How to create a death star style laser in theory.</span><hr size=1> I designed this theoreticly workable death star syle super<br>laser weapon  20 years go or so.<br>(Let us recognize the great technological  power of the Galactic empire where super laser weaponry is concerned)<br><br>Tim <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#484848><td nowrap width=20% v